Document: RDUniform
Path: godot/classes/class_rduniform.rst
Summary: Methods for managing RIDs in a uniform buffer including adding, clearing, and retrieving RID collections.

Method: add_id(id: RID) → void. Adds the given RID to the uniform buffer.

Method: clear_ids() → void. Removes all RIDs from the uniform buffer.

Method: get_ids() → Array[RID] const. Returns a read-only array containing all RIDs currently stored in the uniform buffer.
